name: oriental funk 2.5D v2
description:
Recommendation prompt: mecha_hanbok,techwear_hanbok,mechanical arm, (It doesn't matter if you change the hanbok to another costume)

In the previous version, there was an error that Hanbok was not implemented properly.

It was caused by the mixture of men's and women's hanbok.

In this version, you can distinguish between Hanbok, Hanfu, and Kimono.

and merged urban samurai lora here.

good luck
